    <item>
      <title>迪拜对加密货币投资营销采取更严格的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/dubai-adopts-stricter-rules-around-marketing-crypto-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜加密货币监管机构更新了虚拟资产营销指南，新规则要求公司添加免责声明，澄清此类投资的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/dubai-adopts-stricter-rules-around-marketing-crypto-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
